The big words were not lacking in the letter from the WestLB steering committee to the employees of the house.
By a union of the entities of the Düsseldorf financial institute with the Deka-Bank of Frankfurt, "the central financial market institution of the Sparkasse financial group" could be formed, according to the letter made public on Monday.
